column4: "She stood to answer. "He shall be called Rhaego;" she said; using the words that Jhiqui"
"screamed. "Rhaego; Rhaego; Rhaego!"  The name was still ringing in her ears as Khal Drogo"
"flames made the great monuments seem almost alive.  "What is meaning; name Rhaego?" Khal Drogo"
"the swell of her stomach. "I named him Rhaego."  "A name to make the Usurper"
"named him Rhaego."  "A name to make the Usurper's blood run cold."  Suddenly Doreah"
"make this gift to you for what you did.  "And to Rhaego son of Drogo"
"thrashed and groaned in the night. Dany could see how drawn his face had become. Rhaego"
"and my child." Why had she not remembered the child until now? "My son ï¿½ Rhaego"
"she could feel Rhaego receding from her; as if he had never been.  Ser Jorah"
"feel Rhaego receding from her; as if he had never been.  Ser Jorah and Mirri"
